import React, { Component } from "react";
import Card from "react-bootstrap/Card";

class IndexInfo extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <React.Fragment>
        <Card bg="light" style={{ width: "18rem" }}>
          <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>Current Level</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{index.currentValue}</Card.Text>
          </Card.Body>
        </Card>

        <Card bg="light" style={{ width: "18rem" }}>
          <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>1 Hour Variation</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{returns.h1}</Card.Text>
          </Card.Body>
        </Card>

        <Card bg="light" style={{ width: "18rem" }}>
          <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>24 Hour Variation</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{returns.h24}</Card.Text>
          </Card.Body>
        </Card>

        <Card bg="light" style={{ width: "18rem" }}>
          <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>1 Month Variation</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{returns.MtD}</Card.Text>
          </Card.Body>
        </Card>

        <Card bg="light" style={{ width: "18rem" }}>
          <Card.Body>
            <Card.Title>1 Year Variation</Card.Title>
            <Card.Text>{returns.YtD}</Card.Text>
          </Card.Body>
        </Card>
      </React.Fragment>
    );
  }
}

export default IndexInfo;
